If you’d told me a year ago that I would be the face of an International Brand’s clothing collection, I’d think you were delulu. If you had told me I would fly to Spain, curate my own Basics collection with @mango, have it listed on one of the biggest e-retail platforms in India, @myntra, I’d say “hosh mein ho kya bhai??”

But here we are 🥺 my Basics Collection : Vagmita x Mango is out on Myntra for you to shop, wear and love! Batana kaisa laga ❤️

Special thanks to @kejalparekh for the opportunity and @praachikapse for being the pillar of support throughout! @sabinahalder for the stunnnning looks and the entire camera crew for the gorgeous pictures and videos ✨

latestPosts.caption:
In school I would sneakily read my mum’s Cosmo magazines and marvelled at the glamorous world I saw in them. In college I would walk by stands displaying its latest editions and thought what it would be like to see my face in one of them. Two years ago I wrote on my vision board: I want to be featured in Cosmopolitan magazine. And here we are 🥺 Jiji Gang, you make my dreams come alive every single day. And no matter what I write here won’t be enough to express my gratitude for you ❤️
